            <h2>Benefits </h2>
            <p>Bank of America cares about its associates and offers world class benefits which include:</p>
            <p>
            <ul>
            <li>Employee-focused work environment</li>
            <li>Global Rewards and Recognition programs</li>
            <li>Performance bonus</li>
            <li>Cafeteria subsidy/Food Vouchers</li>
            <li>Private insurance</li>
            <li>Multiple and varied career opportunities</li>
            </ul>
            </p>
            <p><i>Benefits may be modified from time to time by BA Continuum Mexico & Costa Rica Limitada.</i></p>
            <div id="CultureAndWork"></div>
            <h2>Culture and Work Environment</h2>
            <p>At BA Continuum, associates are part of a diverse, global banking environment with best-in-class people, processes and practices. Associates serve Bank of America customers, but also support associates based around the world:  from the U.S. to Asia and in Latin America.</p>
            
                <p>
                    <img src="images/Silvina.jpg" alt="Silvina Salazar, Managing Director" title="Silvina Salazar, Managing Director"/></p>
                <p align="justify">
                    &quot;At Bank of America, we build an inclusive environment where all associates have the opportunity to be successful; it is up to each one of us to take it and perform to the best of our abilities. Together we can achieve our company goals and build a career.&quot;
                </p>
                <p class="style16 text_bold">
                   Silvina Salazar<br />
                    Managing Director
                </p>
                <p>Bank of America is committed to becoming the employer of choice in Costa Rica and Mexico, through a firm commitment to its associates, dedication to the community and by living its corporate values.</p>
                <p>
                    <img src="images/David.jpg" alt="David Catenazzo, Managing Director" title="David Catenazzo, Managing Director"/></p>
                <p align="justify">
                    &quot;Our associates are the core element of our delivery model.  We trust our talent and provide opportunities for career growth and learning.&quot;</p>
                <p class="style16 text_bold" />
                David Catenazzo  <br />
                Managing Director</p>
                
                <p>Bank of America believes that global innovation demands diverse employees and attractive work/life initiatives that sustain and retain them. At BA Continuum, associates can get more than a temporary job, they can begin a career.</p>
               
                <br clear="all" />
            </td>
